text: Comite Creek is a stream in the U.S. states of Louisiana and Mississippi. It is a tributary to the Comite River. The origin of the name "Comite Creek" is obscure. Comite may be a corruption of the name of Amite as in Amite River. Variant names are "Comite River" and "East Fork Comite River". ==References== Category:Rivers of Louisiana Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of East Feliciana Parish, Louisiana Category:Bodies of water of Amite County, Mississippi
